summary: Doing my Dany reread in ADWD I’m starting to think Quaithe is leading Dany into her role as the “villain”. I have a hard time...
body:
Doing my Dany reread in ADWD I’m starting to think Quaithe is leading Dany into her role as the “villain”. I have a hard time imagining Dany is going to become a villain on her own if anything Quaithe is leading her down a path of paranoia, and she is hardening her against potential allies (Quentyn and Tyrion especially). I just think something is going on with whoever Quaithe is, and am really struggling to believe she’s really helping Dany. 

How paranoid Dany becomes after the Quaithe telling her to “trust no one” has really sat with me. It makes me feel that the magically forces moving Dany are probably going to be her downfall.
